                     <summary>I) Gadla Gabra Manfas Qǝddus (fols. 1ra-25vb, 36ra-55vb, 65ra-75rb), possibly incomplete, some fols. are misplaced &#xD;
                        II) Taʾāmra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus: 13 miracles (fols. 26ra-35vb, 56ra-66vb)&#xD;
                        &#xD;
                        Additiones 1-4.</summary>
