                           <date>18th century</date>
                           <persName role="scribe" ref="PRS00000">Walda Takla Hāymānot</persName>Walda Takla Hāymānot is mentioned as the scribe in the supplication formulas: <locus target="32vb">32vb</locus>, 36rb, 55vb.
                           <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist and other saints; names of the donors; name of the scribe; incipit of Text I and its sections; groups of lines (alternating with black lines) on the incipit page of Text II; incipits of the miracles; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
